data.description: How about a place for you and ''them''?Whoever ''them'' is to you, parent/s, friend/s, family, this beautiful 4br well maintained ranch home may be a great set up for you ALL!Sitting on 4.91 acres in a quiet area with separate in-law living quarters, both sides having a very similar lay-out, each offering a full kitchen, 2 bedrooms, living room, and a bathroom.  Enjoy the scenery and watching the wild life (deer, turkey, etc) off of one of the two decks as you you sip your morning coffee or just relax through out the day.Ample parking out front, side, or outback with the back parking having easy, no stair, access through the breezeway separating house from in-law quarters. Ask me (Cory Lehman) about a low 5.75% interest assumable mortgage, and to set up your private tour today!
